## 數據分析功能

### 學習進度分析
```php
class LearningAnalytics {
    public function getStudentProgress($userId) {
        return [
            'coding_time' => $this->getTotalCodingTime($userId),
            'code_quality' => $this->analyzeCodeQuality($userId),
            'participation' => $this->getParticipationRate($userId),
            'improvement' => $this->getImprovementTrend($userId)
        ];
    }
    
    public function getClassOverview($roomId) {
        return [
            'average_progress' => $this->getAverageProgress($roomId),
            'common_errors' => $this->getCommonErrors($roomId),
            'active_students' => $this->getActiveStudents($roomId),
            'completion_rate' => $this->getCompletionRate($roomId)
        ];
    }
}
```

